# ── Terraform internals — never commit ───────────────────────
**/.terraform/
**/.terraform.lock.hcl
**/local.tfplan
crash.log
crash.*.log

# ── State files — remote backend only, never local ───────────
**/terraform.tfstate
**/terraform.tfstate.backup
**/.terraform.tfstate.lock.info

# ── Local secrets — gitignored, use local.tfvars.example ─────
# These contain SSH keys and storage account IDs
**/local.tfvars
**/local.auto.tfvars

# ── Terraform tfvars ─────────────────────────────────────────
# **/terraform.tfvars

# What IS committed:
# ✓ terraform.tfvars — all non-secret values, safe to commit
# ✓ local.tfvars.example — template showing expected format

